## Oracle Machine Learning Notebooks: My First Notebook Example

In this notebook you will learn basic notebook behavior and SQL functions using the *Sales History* (SH) schema data. These examples highlight basic data selection and data vewing using Oracle Autonomous Database. For the machine learning examples, please see companion notebooks.
